{"tid":646243,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] 黃明志《胡志明的雨》粵語版","createTime":"2018-04-29T00:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T10:27:45.000Z","uid":55800,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb5402ffaa5b3f44e41708f173da169b2c6e651","tid":646243,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"細佬第一次改詞，大家俾啲意見，不過盡量屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原曲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rLyvWozGZOs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrLyvWozGZOs&d=rkM8dvoGC4zeQMu%2F0UsLqZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b33d17fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rLyvWozGZOs</a><br />\n<br />\n改詞：<br />\n回頭望過去我倆<br />\n是美好那年華<br />\n城庯<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(注)</span>內那會害怕<br />\n未懼歷遍風沙<br />\n站在路上任風雨吹打<br />\n明瞭徒然仍依依念掛<br />\n仍願背上這代價<br />\n孤身再度南下<br />\n<br />\n紅牆下盼再會妳<br />\n在記憶裏覓尋<br />\n然而又怕碰面了<br />\n你卻沒有聲音<br />\n昨日共聚舊都那中心<br />\n難遺忘然而天色漸暗<br />\n明日冷空氣漸滲<br />\n剩我獨枕孤衾<br />\n<br />\n圍城內雨水中的身影<br />\n彈指間看不清<br />\n幻化的妳消失在背景<br />\n浮沉在雨水中的倒影<br />\n何不早點清醒<br />\n悔不當初的我卻未明(讓這偏執的我變泥濘)<br />\n<br />\n永未明 永未明<br />\n這大城這大雨可會讓我停<br />\n妳薄情 似酷刑<br />\n我願能再度挽手永未怨命<br />\n<br />\n諗返當初妳話過一生一世 喺一齊<br />\n但就揼低一切令我失去自己痛哭流涕<br />\n身體 變差因為我日日喊到力竭聲嘶<br />\n冇計 冇妳喺身邊只能用尼古丁代替<br />\n寄居 喺陌生嘅街區 一堆褪色堡壘<br />\n好似一個空殼終日用酒精將自己麻醉<br />\n唔係話非妳不娶 只想妳答我一句<br />\n結束我嘅空虛<br />\n<br />\n注：城庯(Th&agrave;nh phố)，越南文入面城市嘅意思。中文入面本身係冇「庯」呢個字，亦冇準確嘅讀音，但粵語讀音大概應該係pou4，即係同「蒲」同音。"},{"pid":"83085f390b3cc9595c40d713810e71ed899afca9","tid":646243,"uid":80567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"改歌post已經唔似高登咁受歡迎了<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"bf85cdd4980a32de94ff2b224ab610310ebc9f92","tid":646243,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83085f390b3cc9595c40d713810e71ed899afca9","tid":646243,"uid":80567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"改歌post已經唔似高登咁受歡迎了<br />\n支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed2e5699596a4901abfccd7ea2876d1f046d7b2","tid":646243,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43798ca25c70b2fc12cf40b036fee826a534b448","tid":646243,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:50:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1c2949f86b9f5b69ff72944bfbcec259b85349a","tid":646243,"uid":40429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:52:23.000Z","msg":"黃明志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28efd793a191eaba4829c3e89fc999e4c443a2aa","tid":646243,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c2949f86b9f5b69ff72944bfbcec259b85349a","tid":646243,"uid":40429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:52:23.000Z","msg":"黃明志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"善巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becc42bdc385099ce5a0137f2634ec4dbd2f390f","tid":646243,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac4ed297f9047fb9f5b684863a5e5dea3537941","tid":646243,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032599a790c1dc417a75a29ae33c0adf3c7ceb9e","tid":646243,"uid":26878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:15:57.000Z","msg":"g 持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c685d13cba13e6b8ee675a20f7c166535ac7f6f","tid":646243,"uid":1408